The paper deals with wireless communication and signal processing techniques, which are typically covered in the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories. The use of coding and modulation schemes suggests a focus on Multimedia (cs.MM) and the use of a wireless testbed suggests a focus on Architecture (cs.AR).
